Share this on WhatsAppSpread the loveTijani Olagunju has confessed to killing three people to rise up the food chain in his group.
Murdering three rivals now pushed him up the second position in in the Ilorin zone of his cult.
Tijani said he killed them with the pistol of his late Army Captain father AbdulAzeez Olagunju.
The Uni-Ilorin varsity drop-out was paraded by the Kwara State Police Command in Ilorin.
He said that after joining the group in 2019, his gang members assigned him to be the executioner of rival cult members durig clashes.
